title: Videohive - After Effects Project Files - 3D Text Opener
description:
Perfect for title/text opener. Easy to edit just follow the video tutorial included in the project.

Main Features

Full HD 1080p and HD 720p 23.976fps
After Effects CS5 or higher
3 Template in 1
Required Element 3D v1.6 plugin
If you have Pro Shaders you can achieve the grunge metal in the demo (Optional)
15 sec animation
Video Tutorial Included (Text editing, texture settings and more)
Fast Render times
